0萬持BNO港人更長的逗留時間和可以在英國工作，為未來成為英國公民提供一條途徑。此外，與美英共同發表聲援香港聲明的加拿大和澳洲，同樣可向港人發移民簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWSJ強調，香港是西方自治政府對抗中國霸權主義的全球抗爭最前線。美國面臨的最大挑戰是在不損害本身國家利益的情況下，對違反全球規則的中國施加制裁。將香港人才帶到美國將會損害中國，但同時又會增強美國。而對於競逐連任的特朗普來說，這樣大膽的舉動會令批評者震驚，從而帶來額外的選舉優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200530/MUVHS24JA2GFETE4WEXWAFBJSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200530%2FMUVHS24JA2GFETE4WEXWAFBJSM%2F&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD3za4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=e577a784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200530%2FMUVHS24JA2GFETE4WEXWAFBJSM%2F&h=d009f1b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200530/MUVHS24JA2GFETE4WEXWAFBJSM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"WSJ強調，香港是西方自治政府對抗中國霸權主義的全球抗爭最前線。"},{"pid":"843a5904e2dc5b1547d01a2f87474437dd0a2483","tid":2043049,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd4853714bd579d2e9d3cf1c931e0eda342a477","tid":2043049,"uid":31151,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"WSJ估計，即使獲得綠卡，大多數港人仍會選擇留在香港，因為這才是他們真正的家。但綠卡可以讓他們知道有路可退，會令他們更有信心留港，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b484cde30dcff9b2261229f990d225de6d803a8","tid":2043049,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c588558f8267c01abbf5440b6c2f87dafe1ff2b","tid":2043049,"uid":177639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e2d1b8400c9d24cd15a3a1eea71c3158125011b9","tid":2043049,"uid":305083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:24:48.